HERO_SUBTITLE: Where cigarette butts come alive to brawl
CONTACT_FORM_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Let's talk about bringing your ash tray combat dreams to life!
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is Ash Tray Fighting Game?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Ash Tray Fighting Game is a unique and quirky fighting game where players battle using ordinary ash trays as weapons and arenas.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Choose your favorite ash tray character and master unique combos and special moves. Flick ash, hurl butts, and knock out opponents across gritty environments.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What platforms is it available on?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Ash Tray Fighting Game is currently available on PC, PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch. Mobile versions are in development.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is there an online multiplayer mode?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, you can challenge friends or random players to intense ash tray battles in online ranked and casual multiplayer modes.
CTA_BODY: In this gritty fighting game, ash trays become deadly weapons. Unleash brutal combos and rise through the ranks of underground brawlers.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our unique fighting game
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is the Ash Tray Fighting Game?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: It's a quirky and offbeat fighting game where the characters are everyday objects like ashtrays, lighters, and cigarette butts. Despite their mundane appearances, they come to life and battle in arenas like desktops and coffee tables.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Each character has its own unique move set inspired by its real-world object. An ashtray might be able to spray ashes, while a lighter can breathe fire. The goal is to knock out your opponent using these bizarre attacks.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What platforms is it available on?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: The Ash Tray Fighting Game is currently available to download on PC, PlayStation, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, there is a fully voiced story campaign that follows the misadventures of these inanimate objects coming to life. Expect a healthy dose of dark humor and parodies of classic fighting game storylines.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I unlock new characters and arenas?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Absolutely! By completing different modes and challenges, you can unlock additional fighters like pens, pencils, and paper clips as well as environments like office spaces and living rooms.
PAGE_DETAIL_1_VALUE: Experience visceral hand-to-hand battles between everyday ashtrays. Shatter rivals with savage combos and unlock devastating special moves.
PAGE_DETAIL_2_VALUE: Follow the journey of an unassuming ashtray seeking revenge against the criminal syndicate that wronged its maker.
PAGE_DETAIL_3_VALUE: Choose from a diverse cast of ashtrays, each with their own unique fighting styles and explosive personalities.
STARTER_TEMPLATE_FOOTER_CONTENT: Experience the intense, smoky battles between scrappy ash trays in a fighting game like no other. Who will emerge victorious in the Cinders Clash?

TESTIMONIAL_3_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: From the gritty arenas to the diverse roster of ashtray fighters, this game nails the ashtray brawler vibe perfectly.
